title: Test LaTeX Error 2
description: LaTeX compilation failed with missing package error

attempts.solution: Root cause: Missing LaTeX package 'tikz'. Solution: Added \usepackage{tikz} to document preamble. Testing: Verified compilation succeeds. Prevention: Added package validation to build process.

final_solution: Root cause: Missing LaTeX package 'tikz'. Solution: Added \usepackage{tikz} to document preamble. Testing: Verified compilation succeeds. Prevention: Added package validation to build process.
